{
	"name": "Gerrin Deerstalker",
	"type": "hero",
	"system": {
		"promise": 0,
		"description": "<p><span class=\"litm--ingress\">A SPIRITED WOODLAND HUNTSMAN DEDICATED ABOVE ALL TO HIS FAMILY.</span></p><blockquote><p>\"Shhhh.... quiet. Can you hear it?... It's everywhere. The forest. It has its own life, its own breath. Sometimes I sit here alone, like this, and just fall into it. It feels like plunging into a chilly, clear pond. I'm somehow more awake, more... here. I can hear every critter squeak and every reindeer huff. And deeper, the crawling and teeming in every rotten log and every creaking branch. And I can hear the wind, ruffling the leaves like my mother used to ruffle my hair. This forest is alive, and we are nothing but its lucky houseguests.\"</p></blockquote>",
