				"isScratched": false,
				"description": "<p>High in the tree-covered mountains of Hartland, deep in the Shady Forest, there lives a young deer stalker named Gerrin. Leading the simple life of a hunter, he sets out every day deep into the woods to hunt and provide for his family. Sometimes he's gone for days at a time, living under the dense canopy in solitary tranquility. For he loves the forest and respects it and guards it as a steward.</p>",
