				"isScratched": false,
				"description": "<p>Before he left their home on a matter of importance he never explained, Gerrin's father gave him a well-crafted curved bow made out of the boughs of a yew tree, sacred and known for its protective properties. \"It will serve you well, but only if you master it,\" said Father. Since then, Gerrin has practiced without ceasing, honing his archery further and further, and gaining a reputation among the woodland hunters.</p>",
