				"isScratched": false,
				"description": "<p>Since the day he was born, Gerrin had a special spark to him. His mother told him many times that she's seen it in his eyes as a child and that the local Wise One had always looked at him differently: approvingly, perhaps, but also with a touch of concern. Gerrin grew up to be a fierce boy, unyielding and stubborn, but with a great force of life. Something within him shines through.</p>",
