				"isScratched": false,
				"description": "<p>Gerrin lives in a mountainside cabin with his mother, grandfather, and little brother Chippie. Except for his forest forays and for a special annual trip they take to the nearby hamlet of Hartwood, these three are his entire world. His mother's wise advice and knowing looks, his grandfather's ramblings about ancient kingdoms, and Chippie's little pranks and stunts - he cherishes these things above all else.</p>",
